
Últimas coisas:


Criar a inicialização do software na BBB:


Create /etc/init/myjob.conf

vi /etc/init/myjob.conf
with content like the following

description     "my job"
start on startup
task
exec /path/to/my/script.sh

mais: https://askubuntu.com/questions/228304/how-do-i-run-a-script-at-start-up